Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:46.26,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to show
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:50.26,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cut open my skull look into my head
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:53.14,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why I'm so harsh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:54.83,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be so brash
