Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:01:00.04,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:06.82,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't always show my everything to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:10.90,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If this moment was for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:14.41,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I try to hear,lend my ear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.41,0:01:20.40,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Voices inside one link to join it all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:21.83,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:37.79,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:44.52,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't always show my everything to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:48.58,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If this moment was for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.66,0:01:52.03,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I try to hear,lend my ear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:58.08,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Voices inside one link to join it all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:01.31,Op-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it goes
